    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, you become an avatar of peace, which gives you two benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You have resistance to all damage dealt by other creatures (their attacks, spells, and other effects).</li>\n<li>Whenever a creature hits you with an attack, it takes radiant damage equal to half the damage you take from the attack.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you attack a creature, cast a spell on it, or deal damage to it by any means but this feature, neither benefit works against that creature until you finish a long rest.</p>",
